ers are all that will keep you alive while exploring the hostile surface of the planet Valaka. Work together to complete objectives, acquire resources, build and defend a base, and then escape to the extraction point together.\n\nWould you like to know more? \n\nAlways keep in mind that each and every mod is completely free, so you can try them all until you find your favorite Starship Troopers: Extermination mods.\nAnd of course, the important thing is to have fun with these Starship Troopers: Extermination mods - using them to create a personalized game experience that’s best for you.","modsCount":0,"downloadsCount":0,"createdAt":1683188223000,"assets":{"iconUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/813/412/638187958674631959.png","tileUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/game-box-art/83644_8aa3cf57-2f81-4bf2-8753-5ff469b3c9da.png","logoUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/game-logos/83644_ec941d00-d547-43dc-b3e3-8838f5057dac.png","coverArtUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/game-covers/83644_7962ad12-62b1-412b-9e13-1bf12ccce4cd.png"}},{"id":84610,"slug":"station-to-station","name":"Station to Station","description":"Station to Station Mods at CurseForge - The Home for the Best Station to Station Mods\n\n‘Station to Station’ is a minimalist \u0026 relaxing game about building railway connections. Grab your conductor’s hat and bring the voxel-art world to life through the magic of trains!\n\nIn Station to Station, your world starts small with a handful of rural structures. Place stations and create connections to foster growth and expansion. As you build more connections, your area will grow, transforming into a vibrant, lush environment full of life and color! To keep you on your toes, the game also features engaging puzzle elements, challenging you to optimize routes and solve logistical conundrums.\n\nYou can easily find the best Station to Station mods here, with each Station to Station mod having its own unique flavor, functionality, and characteristics. Each one offers a